               <msContents>
                  <summary>A compilation of three stories in Pre-Classical Chaghatay written in the
                     post-Mongol or Timurid version of the Old Uyghur script. Originally penned for
                        <persName key="" role="dte"><persName xml:lang="chg">جلال الدین میر
                           چاقماق</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="chg-Latn-x">Jalāl al-dīn Mīr
                        Čaqmaq</persName></persName>, the Timurid amir of Yazd under <persName
                        key="person_24010955"><persName xml:lang="chg">شاهرخ</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="chg-Latn-x">Šāhruḫ</persName></persName>. All three
                     stories are slightly defective, and the folios of many are out of
                     order.</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="chg">Pre-Classical Chaghatay written in the post-Mongol or
                     Timurid version of the Old Uyghur script</textLang>
                  
